'''Brenda''' is a woman who was separated from her children during a parking garage fire.

==History==
Brenda's kids were in the car when she stopped to get some chocolate milk at the store. Instead of bringing them in with her, she left them in the car. While she was gone, a fire started with a hybrid car in the garage. She went back to search for her children, but [[Ben Warren|Ben]] and [[Victoria Hughes|Vic]] stopped her and forced her to leave, assuring her they'd find her kids and get them back to her. Once she was out, they found her kids and evacuated them. Once they were out, they loaded Jonny onto a gurney and took all of them to the hospital.

==Relationships==
===Familial===
She has two children: [[Jonny]] and [[Abby]].
